{"id": 3002, "genre": 1001, "title": "现如今，你觉得一个当代成年人最应该具备的常识是什么？", "description": "来说说你心里“成年之后看待世界的 rule No.1”应该是啥。（题图来自：iStock ©️ CSA-Printstock）", "record_count": 3868, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20190915212442CnwrH9Iu0k5i6Ujm.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-09-16T17:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 346624, "content": "搞清楚常识和道理是两码事", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1012338}, {"id": 346625, "content": "对知识的敬畏", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 927309}, {"id": 346626, "content": "坦诚接受自己的缺陷", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1660558}, {"id": 346627, "content": "不要随便装逼", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1290280}, {"id": 346883, "content": "自律", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1662863}, {"id": 347140, "content": "1不要做没脑子的事。2坚定信念。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1348455}, {"id": 346629, "content": "不要随便站队", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1659769}, {"id": 346630, "content": "物质决定意识", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1012749}, {"id": 346631, "content": "没有谁是应该帮助你的", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1352265}, {"id": 346632, "content": "无知不是单纯。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1444313}, {"id": 346633, "content": "面对粗糙，平凡的自己", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1662375}, {"id": 346634, "content": "有独立的思考，判断能力，而不是盲目跟风。现在的沙雕太多了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1634830}, {"id": 346890, "content": "尊重不同价值观的人，不以自己的价值判断揣度绑架他人", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1662884}, {"id": 346636, "content": "态度决定一切", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1662381}, {"id": 346637, "content": "认清自己到死也是孤独的，下一秒自己就有可能死去。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1310513}, {"id": 346638, "content": "接受自己的平庸", "image": null, "praise_count": 59, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1486945}, {"id": 346639, "content": "不要麻烦", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1662390}, {"id": 347919, "content": "学会自己百度", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1612212}, {"id": 346641, "content": "要有逻辑推理能力，要有实事求是的精神，要经常换位思考", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 412114}, {"id": 347921, "content": "多数人的意见并不应该代表少数人的意见，尤其是涉及个体利益时。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1650678}, {"id": 346642, "content": "不要先声夺人，斩钉截铁式地说话，要谦卑", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1555771}, {"id": 346643, "content": "少当网络上的喷子现实中的怂b", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1085800}, {"id": 346899, "content": "阶级是真实存在的，接受就好", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1662892}, {"id": 346644, "content": "从来如此，便对么？", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1573201}, {"id": 346645, "content": "不论在什么行业，了解世界的发展方向及大致的运行规律", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 952931}, {"id": 346647, "content": "世界在不停变化中，唯有持续不断学习，才能认识和适应不断变化着的世界。要活到老学到老。\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1662107}, {"id": 346648, "content": "识相", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 666852}, {"id": 346904, "content": "别利用网络传播自己的无知言论", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1599015}, {"id": 346649, "content": "自私", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1660038}, {"id": 346651, "content": "不断学习，终身成长", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 914221}, {"id": 346652, "content": "谦虚 包容", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1364089}, {"id": 346653, "content": "有自己的世界观", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1583360}, {"id": 346654, "content": "在人际交往中，需要体面、得体；只有在正确的时间，做合适的事、说恰当的话，生活才得以继续。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1657929}, {"id": 346655, "content": "不能把“我以为”，当做理所当然", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1662403}, {"id": 346656, "content": "理解共情。\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1160401}, {"id": 346657, "content": "做好自己，保持独立。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 904726}, {"id": 346658, "content": "努力", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1247681}, {"id": 346659, "content": "爱情只是生活中的一件小事。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 515073}, {"id": 346915, "content": "没有什么是应该具备的 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1131733}, {"id": 346660, "content": "爱情的魔力", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1662413}, {"id": 346916, "content": "同理心", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1515557}, {"id": 346661, "content": "不是所有感受都能一样", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1662414}, {"id": 346663, "content": "最匮乏的常识是明白自己的没有常识🤔", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1547449}, {"id": 346664, "content": "不盲从，独立思考", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1612126}, {"id": 347176, "content": "自己的世界，别人的世界和真实的世界，可能都是不一样的", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 821386}, {"id": 346665, "content": "动机和效果是两码事", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1662417}, {"id": 346921, "content": "世界不是你想的那么好，也不是你想的那么差。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1352833}, {"id": 346666, "content": "帮你是情分，不帮你是本分", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1437145}, {"id": 346667, "content": "要对自己的选择负责", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1437145}, {"id": 346923, "content": "宽阔的眼界，不用自己的世界中的规则要求别人", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1501018}]}